		{
			dependencies: ["3331CF8114EA836C"]
			description: [
				"You may have noticed a lot of vermin running around at night. But the Ultimate Zookeeper taught us that every animal is beautiful in its own way. Even the rats."
				""
				"And there are a lot of &aRats&r. They are filthy. They steal your crops and food. But they are also very intelligent. They may well turn out to be the key to this whole enterprise."
				""
				"Like hostile mobs, they spawn in the dark, particularly on top of &9garbage&r blocks. But first you'll need cheese..."
			]
