			dependencies: ["7A2C02287D85FC14"]
			description: [
				"To tame a &aRat&r, you will need a lot of &9cheese&r. To make cheese, pour &9milk&r into a &9cauldron&r and wait a bit. Throw the cheese pieces to a rat repeatedly to tame it (it may take 10-20 pieces)."
				""
				"Do make sure to tame more than one. You'll need a male and a female to really get your rat colony going."
